Enter the odometer reading: 25.5
Enter the number of gallons used:
Fillup #3
Enter the odometer reading: 30.5
Enter the number of gallons used:
Fillup #4
Enter the odometer reading: 35.5
Enter the number of gallons used:
Fillup #5
Enter the odometer reading: 40.5
Enter the number of gallons used:
Fillup #6
Enter the odometer reading: 45.5
Enter the number of gallons used:
Average MPG: 14.33
